<list_item><loc_73><loc_360><loc_460><loc_396>b Background Investigation refers to the verification of an behaviour, and previous performance, if any, by validating the information and records declared by the applicant in their Personal Data Sheet (PDS) such as contacting their identified reference person/s in their current or previous workplace or through other means /methods.</list_item>
