<text><loc_49><loc_388><loc_457><loc_439>35. An Open Ranking System shall be adopted to ensure transparency in the process and results of the comparative assessment wherein applicants or subset of applicants are present to witness the actual evaluation for which the scores of all applicants present thereat shall be disclosed to all attendees. Each applicant shall also be given an opportunity to ask questions and seek clarifications on the results of their individual assessment and acknowledge their individual results during the receipt of the individual   results, applicants shall affix their  signature on their Individual Evaluation Sheet (IES) (see prescribed template in Annex G-2) Upon</text>
